&lt;p>Although many users may not realize it, all bitcoin wallets need some level of maintenance to be properly managed. If you’re using a custodian, they take care of these things. However, when you hold your bitcoin in self-custody, no one is responsible for managing your wallet but you. To maintain your wallet properly, you’ll need to know what UTXOs are and how to manage them.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Too Many UTXOs: How To Avoid High Fees</title><link>https://21ideas.org/en/protocol/utxo-2/</link><pubDate>Wed, 03 Aug 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://21ideas.org/en/protocol/utxo-2/</guid><description>&lt;div class="book-expand">
