&lt;p>Building on our first article covering &lt;a href="https://21ideas.org/en/protocol/utxo-1">what UTXOs are and why they matter&lt;/a>, we’ll now dive deeper into various situations where you may need to actively manage the UTXOs in your self-custody wallet. This installment will describe the problems that can arise from accumulating too many UTXOs in your bitcoin wallet, as well as strategies you can use to resolve these issues and prevent them from occurring in the future.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>UTXOs Privacy</title><link>https://21ideas.org/en/protocol/utxo-3/</link><pubDate>Mon, 03 Oct 2022 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://21ideas.org/en/protocol/utxo-3/</guid><description>&lt;div class="book-expand">
